Tushman, M.L.; Anderson, P. (1986). "Technological Discontinuities and Organizational Environments". Administrative Science Quarterly. 31: 439–465. doi:10.2307/2392832. 
Eric Chaniot (2007). "The Red Pill of Technology Innovation" Red Pill, October 2007.


